manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Hasbro Corporate Responsibility Hasbro is committed to being an ethical and responsible company and is a recognized toy industry leader in the areas of product safety, environmental sustainability, ethical sourcing and philanthropy. Baby Alive Face Paint Fairy-African American Baby Alive turns mommy and daddy moments into a magical world of play. Girls get to be like mommy and boys get to be like daddy, experiencing first-hand what it's like to be a parent who is excited, delighted, and surprised by the many ways they can nurture and play. They're more than adorable dolls! Using accessories based on each baby's theme, kids can feed her a bottle, change her diaper when she wets, get her ready for activities, and more. With Baby Alive, kids can experience nurturing play...and love every moment like a mommy or daddy does! Reveal Magical Paint Repeatable Play Drinks and Wets Fairy Dress-Up

Fantastic Face Paint Imagine fun fairy tales with the Baby Alive Face Paint Fairy doll... because girls and boys can simulate painting her face to look like a fairy! First, fill her wand with ice cold water. Then, drag it along her face like a paint brush to reveal a beautiful design -- it looks like face paint! Wipe her face with a warm hand and her face paint magically disappears to repeat the painting play again and again. Feeding and Changing Time Fun Like a real baby, the Face Paint Fairy doll needs mommy or daddy to prepare a bottle for her when it’s time to eat. Kids can experience what it’s like to feed their baby by filling the bottle with tap water and feeding it to her. Yum, looks like she drank it all up…better check her diaper (additional diapers sold separately). Ut oh! She wets too! Kids can change her wet diaper so she can be ready for more play. All better! Fairy Dress Up After her face is painted, kids can complete their baby doll's look with her detachable fairy wings. Dress-up and fantasy play make mommy and daddy moments with the Face Paint Fairy doll magical, too! Tell tales together and imagine fun, playful fairy scenes!
Includes Includes 1 doll, 1 bottle, 1 diaper, 1 set of wings, 1 wand, and 1 removable outfit. Baby Alive and all related properties are trademarks of Hasbro.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Daughter love's talking these on and off her babies
reviews.reviewText: Let me just start by saying, the Baby Alive Diapers Pack is an absolute game-changer for any little caregiver looking after their beloved Baby Alive dolls or any other baby dolls! These diapers are not just diapers; they're the secret ingredient to an immersive and adorable nurturing experience.First and foremost, these diapers are incredibly realistic. They're perfectly sized for Baby Alive dolls, offering a snug fit that's both practical and cute. The designs are adorable, featuring playful patterns that add a touch of charm to every diaper change. From cute animal prints to vibrant colors, these diapers make changing time a fun and engaging activity.The durability of these diapers is impressive. They're well-made, ensuring they withstand multiple changes without losing their shape or functionality. The tabs securely fasten, keeping the diaper in place even during playtime activities, which is a relief for little ones engaged in imaginative role-playing.What's truly fantastic about this pack is the quantity provided. With multiple diapers in one pack, there's an ample supply for extended play sessions, allowing kids to engage in continuous nurturing play without interruption. It's a great relief for parents, too, as they won't need to worry about running out of diapers anytime soon!Moreover, these diapers offer more than just a practical function. They encourage imaginative play and nurturing instincts in children. It's heartwarming to witness kids taking care of their dolls, mimicking real-life caregiving experiences while fostering empathy and responsibility.Additionally, these diapers are part of the Baby Alive ecosystem, making them a perfect addition to any Baby Alive doll collection. They enhance the play experience, adding an extra layer of authenticity and engagement to the nurturing process.In summary, the Baby Alive Diapers Pack is a must-have accessory for any child who loves caring for their dolls. With their adorable designs, durability, and quantity provided, these diapers enhance the nurturing play experience, sparking hours of joy, creativity, and imaginative fun.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 20, 2016
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute for Baby Alive dolls
reviews.reviewText: My daughter has been wanting these diapers for a long time. She has three Baby Alive dolls and two wet so I decided to go ahead and get these. They are great for the dolls and fit well. They are well made and high quality. For the price, I will still just use the premmie diapers rather than get more of these. The diapers are cute and make her happy so I am happy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2019
reviews.reviewText: These cute little diapers worked out perfect for my cousin’s little. She wanted the Baby Alive doll which we purchased these in addition. She loved the idea her doll could eat and than potty.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 1, 2020
reviews.reviewText: These diapers are great for 12-14" dolls. If you keep tabs on designated areas they can be used over and over again. We have not used these with dolls that actually wet so I don't know how absorbent they are. This was a good value for my 2 year old granddaughter who loves to dress and undress her dolls; including their diapers.

reviews.reviewTitle: Perfect for the doll, as described.
reviews.reviewText: Not a knock off. Its the actual Baby Alive brand. Fit the doll perfectly and work as they should
